        <mxCell id="input_payload" value="속성: Frontend Payload&#xa;이름: UI Design Generate Request&#xa;역할: 프론트에서 n8n으로 전달되는 생성 요청&#xa;주요 데이터: md, promo, simpleBrief, sectionInputs, design, output" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9F0;strokeColor=#E7A94B;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="180" width="300" height="145" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_01" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Generate Promo UI Design&#xa;역할: Webhook 요청 수신&#xa;주요 출력: body, headers" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="470" y="180" width="300" height="130" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_02" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Normalize Payload&#xa;역할: 입력값 정규화 및 필수값 검증&#xa;주요 출력: id, model, imageModel, md, promo, template, simpleBrief, sectionInputs, design" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="870" y="180" width="330" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_03" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Load UI Design Image Prompt&#xa;역할: UI 디자인 이미지 생성용 프롬프트 템플릿 로딩&#xa;주요 출력: prompt, prompt id, prompt version" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="470" y="400" width="300" height="145" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_04" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Build UI Design Prompt&#xa;역할: 정규화된 입력과 프롬프트 템플릿을 병합해 LLM 요청 생성&#xa;주요 출력: designBrief, layoutMapping seed, llmRequest, promptMeta" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="870" y="400" width="330" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="brief" value="속성: Intermediate Data&#xa;이름: designBrief&#xa;역할: LLM에 전달되는 통합 디자인 생성 지시 데이터&#xa;주요 데이터: sectionInputs, simpleBrief, requiredContent, designStyle, mdConceptSummary, mdPromptContext, mdConceptJson, mdSummary" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9F0;strokeColor=#E7A94B;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1260" y="400" width="350" height="175" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_05" value="속성: n8n HTTP Request Node&#xa;노드 이름: LLM Generate Image Prompt&#xa;역할: designBrief 기반 LLM 호출 요청 생성/전송&#xa;주요 출력: LLM raw response" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="680" width="300" height="145" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="llm_service" value="속성: External AI Service&#xa;이름: LLM&#xa;역할: designBrief를 해석해 이미지 생성용 상세 프롬프트 구조 생성&#xa;주요 출력: imagePrompt, negativePrompt, designBrief, layoutMapping, mdComplianceMap" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EAF7F7;strokeColor=#4AA3A3;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="850" width="300" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_06" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Parse Validate Image Prompt&#xa;역할: LLM 응답 JSON 파싱 및 필수 구조 검증&#xa;주요 출력: final imagePrompt, designBrief, layoutMapping, mdComplianceMap" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="470" y="680" width="330" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_07" value="속성: AI/API Call&#xa;노드 이름: Generate UI Design Image&#xa;역할: 최종 imagePrompt로 UI 디자인 이미지 생성&#xa;주요 출력: image URL 또는 b64 image data" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EAF7F7;strokeColor=#4AA3A3;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="870" y="680" width="330" height="145" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_08" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Store UI Design Result&#xa;역할: 이미지 생성 결과와 생성 메타데이터를 n8n 결과 구조로 정리&#xa;주요 출력: imageUrl, designUrl, imagePrompt, designBrief, layoutMapping, mdComplianceMap, payload" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1260" y="680" width="350" height="165" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_09" value="속성: Storage/API Call&#xa;노드 이름: Persist UI Design Asset&#xa;역할: 이미지와 메타데이터를 Vercel API로 전달해 Blob + DB 저장&#xa;주요 출력: assetUrl, imageUrl, designUrl, runId, assetId" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EFFFF4;strokeColor=#55A56A;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="930" width="330" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="node_10" value="속성: n8n Node&#xa;노드 이름: Merge Persisted UI Design Result&#xa;역할: n8n 생성 결과와 저장 API 응답 병합&#xa;주요 출력: persisted result payload" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F1ECFF;strokeColor=#8A6EDB;fontSize=13;align=left;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="470" y="930" width="330" height="145" as="geometry" />
